import "./PropertyList.css"; import useFetch from "../../hooks/useFetch"; const PropertyList = () => { const { data, loading, error } = useFetch("/hotels/countByType"); return (
{loading?("list is loading"):(

Hotels

{data[0]?.count} hotels

Apartments

{data[1]?.count} apartments

Resorts

{data[2]?.count} resorts

Villas

{data[3]?.count} villas

Cabins

{data[4]?.count} cabins

) }
); }; export default PropertyList;
